<article>
    <h1>$150,000 worth of Black Fri&#xAD;day vouch&#xAD;ers in SPH news&#xAD;pa&#xAD;pers</h1>
    <h2></h2>
    <section>
        <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/textview" title="The Straits Times">The Straits Times</a>
        - <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/20201126/textview" title="The Straits Times - 2020-11-26"><time>2020-11-26</time></a>
        - <span>FRONT PAGE</span>
        - <span role="byline"></span>
    </section>

    <p>The year’s most an­tic­i­pated week­end sale kicks off with Sin­ga­pore Press Hold­ings (SPH) news­pa­pers fea­tur­ing more than $150,000 worth of shop­ping vouch­ers from par­tic­i­pat­ing re­tail­ers.</p>
    <p>The SPH Black Fri­day & Cyber Mon­day vouch­ers will be pub­lished to­day and to­mor­row in the daily news­pa­pers The Straits Times broad­sheet, The New Paper tabloid freesheet, the Chi­nese-lan­guage Lianhe Zaobao and the Malay-lan­guage Berita Har­ian.</p>
    <p>For Chi­nese daily Shin Min, vouch­ers will be pub­lished to­day while Lianhe Wan­bao will fea­ture the vouch­ers to­mor­row.</p>
    <p>Top re­tail­ers BHG, Courts, Gain City, Har­vey Nor­man and Metro are giv­ing away six types of shop­ping vouch­ers worth more than $150,000 to SPH read­ers.</p>
    <p>Read­ers can claim the vouch­ers by scan­ning QR codes and cre­at­ing an ac­count on­line. The unique vouch­ers will then be sent to the reader’s e-mail ad­dress.</p>
    <p>Read­ers can claim one each of the fol­low­ing vouch­ers:</p>
    <p>• BHG: $20 off with a min­i­mum of $160 spent</p>
    <p>• Courts: $20 off with $100 spent</p>
    <p>• Gain City: $30 off with $120 spent</p>
    <p>• Gain City: $100 off with $300 spent on mat­tresses (avail­able at Gain City Me­ga­s­tore @ Sungei Kadut)</p>
    <p>• Har­vey Nor­man: $25 off with $100 spent</p>
    <p>• Metro: $10 off with $100 spent</p>
    <p>Af­ter claim­ing the vouch­ers, read­ers can re­deem them at the re­spec­tive re­tail­ers’ stores from to­mor­row to Mon­day.</p>
    <p>The vouch­ers are avail­able in</p>
    <p>lim­ited quan­ti­ties and while stocks last.</p>
    <p>How to claim the vouch­ers</p>
    <p>• Scan one of the QR codes to claimthe voucher of choice</p>
    <p>• Sign up for an ac­count on­line</p>
    <p>• The voucher will be sent to the reader’s e-mail ad­dress</p>
    <p>• Re­deem the voucher in-store from to­mor­row to Mon­day (terms and con­di­tions ap­ply)</p>
    <p>• For more in­for­ma­tion, go to shop­for­good.sph.com.sg/ black-fri­day</p>

